CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 11, 1969, pg. 16 reads:"Social Committee - The hard-working committee responsible for the beautiful holiday ball sponsored by the AKA Sorority, are: seated from left: Sorors Madelyn Hairston, LeeBertha Nicklos, Merline Stewart, Gelora Wilson and Bobble Green. Standing: Delores Gaines, Martha Hunt, Edythe Perkins and Marsolette Fleming. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha members, seated from left: Madelyn Hairston, Lee Bertha Nicklos, Merline Stewart, Gelora Wilson, Bobble Green; standing: Delores Gaines, Martha Hunt, Edythe Perkins, and Marsolette Fleming, posed in William Penn Hotel during holiday formal
